  |              |       |                                        |\
  |              |       |                                        |\
  |             \\!/      |                                        |\
  |              V       |                                        |\
  |           Formato    |                                        |\
  |             /   \\    |                                        |\
  |            /     \\   |                                        |\
  |           /       \\  |                                        |\
  |          /         \\ |                                        |\
  |          |          \\|                                        |\
  |          |           |                                        |\
  |         \\!/         \\!/                                       |\
  |          V           V                                        |\
  |         Myio       Mydefs                                     |\
  |                                                               |\
  |                                                               |\
  | Figure 19.  USES  Graph for program Prog1ui:  a USES graph is |\
  |             a directed acyclic graph.                         |\
  +---------------------------------------------------------------+\
