  | | BLOCK                                               |       |\
  | |                                                     |       |\
  | |    Typeint ('Previous value of i was', i);          |       |\
  | |    0 -> i;                                          |       |\
  | | ENDBLOCK;                                           |       |\
  | +-----------------------------------------------------+       |\
  |                                                               |\
  | +-----------------------------------------------------+       |\
  | | INTERFACE Formato USES Mydefs, Myio;                |       |\
  | |                                                     |       |\
  | | DCL Typeint PROC (format DESC OF VAL Char,          |       |\
